70px indicates the max padding
24px indicates the min padding 
and the calc between need to adjust the exact value on specific viewport to set the padding
e.g the below example shows the conatiner width is 1512px and padding right is 70px and then the screen size reduces the 70px padding reduces to the 24px. 


padding-right: clamp(24px, calc(4.6vw + 1px), 70px);